mostRecent.text: Excellent product from Dell. I have used other banded wireless mouse as well however those were very delicate to use and if you hold dell wireless mouse you will feel its sturdy. Quality is also very good.
mostRecent.title: Worth every penny

mostHelpful.author: Umesh Kumar
mostHelpful.text: Only one big minus point I found its Keyboard display. Extremely disappointed towards this issue. It's very difficult to read the words & digits to read because of its white letters & numerics on steel coloured base. Wherever white letters and numerics on black body is the best . I couldn't use it with it's keyboard. I am using this laptop with the external keyboard purchased from market which is the big reason of my disappointment the purchase of this Laptop cost me with three years warranty Rs. 76000.00 approx and this is a big value.
mostHelpful.title: Worth every penny
